[{"id":"/sicpjs/3.3.2","tag":"TITLE","body":"3.3.2  表示队列"},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p1","child":[{"body":"\n    突变子\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"set_head"},{"body":"\n    和\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"set_tail"},{"body":"\n    使我们能够使用对来构造那些仅靠\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"pair"},{"body":",","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"head"},{"body":",\n    和\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"tail"},{"body":"\n    无法构造的数据结构。  本节展示了如何使用对来表示一种称为队列的数据结构。  第 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.3.3","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.3"},{"body":"节将展示如何表示称为表的数据结构。\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p2","child":[{"body":"\n    一个","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EM","child":[{"body":"队列","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"是一个序列，其中项目在一端插入（称为\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EM","child":[{"body":"尾部","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"）并从另一端删除（称为\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EM","child":[{"body":"头部","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"）。\n    图 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.18","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.18"},{"body":"\n    显示了一个最初为空的队列，其中插入了项目\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a"},{"body":"和","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"b"},{"body":"。随后","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a"},{"body":"被移除，插入了","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"c"},{"body":"和","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"d"},{"body":"，并移除了","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"b"},{"body":"。由于项目总是按照插入顺序被删除，队列有时也称为\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EM","child":[{"body":"FIFO","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"（先进先出）缓冲区。\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FIGURE","table":{"tag":"TABLE","child":[{"tag":"TR","child":[{"tag":"TD","child":[{"body":"\n\t\t操作\n\t      ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TD","child":[{"body":"\n\t\t结果队列\n\t      ","tag":"#text"}]}]},{"tag":"TR","child":[{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"const q = make_queue();"}]},{"tag":"TD"}]},{"tag":"TR","child":[{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"insert_queue(q, \"a\");"}]},{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a"}]}]},{"tag":"TR","child":[{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"insert_queue(q, \"b\");"}]},{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a  b"}]}]},{"tag":"TR","child":[{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"delete_queue(q);"}]},{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"b"}]}]},{"tag":"TR","child":[{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"insert_queue(q, \"c\");"}]},{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"b c"}]}]},{"tag":"TR","child":[{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"insert_queue(q, \"d\");"}]},{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"b c d"}]}]},{"tag":"TR","child":[{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"delete_queue(q);"}]},{"tag":"TD","child":[{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"c d"}]}]}]},"captionHref":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.18","captionName":"Figure 3.18 ","captionBody":[{"body":"队列操作。","tag":"#text"}]}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p3","child":[{"body":"\n    从\n    \n    数据抽象的角度来看，我们可以将队列视为由下列一组操作定义：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"UL","child":[{"tag":"LI","child":[{"body":"\n        一个构造函数：\n        ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"BR"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"make_queue()"},{"tag":"BR"},{"body":"\n          返回一个空队列（即不包含任何项的队列）。\n\t  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"LI","child":[{"body":"\n        一个谓词：\n        ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"BR"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"is_empty_queue("},{"tag":"META","body":"queue"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":")"},{"tag":"BR"},{"body":"\n          用于测试队列是否为空。\n\t  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"LI","child":[{"body":"\n        一个选择器：\n        ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"BR"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"front_queue("},{"tag":"META","body":"queue"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":")"},{"tag":"BR"},{"body":"\n          返回队列前端的对象；如果队列为空则发出错误信号，并且不修改队列。\n\t  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"LI","child":[{"body":"\n        两个变异操作：\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"BR"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"insert_queue("},{"tag":"META","body":"queue"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":", "},{"tag":"META","body":"item"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":")"},{"tag":"BR"},{"body":"\n          在队列尾部插入\n          \n\t  项，并返回修改后的队列作为其值。","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"BR"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"delete_queue("},{"tag":"META","body":"queue"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":")"},{"tag":"BR"},{"body":"\n          移除队列前端的\n          \n\t  项，并返回修改后的队列作为其值；如果删除前队列为空，则发出错误信号。\n      ","tag":"#text"}]}]}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p4","child":[{"body":"\n    由于队列是项目的序列，我们当然可以将其表示为普通列表；队列的前端将是列表的 \n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"head"},{"body":"\n    ，在队列中插入一个项目等同于在列表末尾追加一个新元素，而从队列中删除一个项目则相当于取出列表的 \n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"tail"},{"body":"\n    。然而，这种表示方法效率不高，因为为了插入一个项目，我们必须遍历列表直到到达末尾。由于我们遍历列表的唯一方法是通过连续的 \n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"tail"},{"body":"\n    操作，因此对于包含 ","tag":"#text"},{"body":"$n$","tag":"LATEX"},{"body":" 个项目的列表，这种遍历需要 ","tag":"#text"},{"body":"$\\Theta(n)$","tag":"LATEX"},{"body":" 个步骤。对列表表示方法进行简单修改可以克服这一缺陷，使得队列操作的实现只需 ","tag":"#text"},{"body":"$\\Theta(1)$","tag":"LATEX"},{"body":" 个步骤；也就是说，所需步骤的数量与队列的长度无关。\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p5","child":[{"body":"\n    列表表示方法的问题在于需要扫描以查找列表的末尾。需要扫描的原因在于，尽管将列表表示为一系列对的链这一标准方法能够为我们提供一个指向列表开头的指针，但它却无法提供一个易于访问的指向列表末尾的指针。克服这一缺点的修改方法是将队列表示为一个列表，并附加一个额外的指针，该指针指示列表中的最后一对。这样，在插入项目时，我们就可以查阅尾部指针，从而避免扫描整个列表。\n  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p6","child":[{"body":"\n    队列因此被表示为一对指针，\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"front_ptr"},{"body":"\n    以及\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"rear_ptr"},{"body":",\n    它们分别指示普通列表中的第一对和最后一对。\n    由于我们希望队列是一个可识别的对象，因此可以使用\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"pair"},{"body":"\n    来将这两个指针组合起来。于是，队列本身将是这两个指针的\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"pair"},{"body":"\n   。\n    Figure ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.19","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.19"},{"body":"\n    说明了这种表示方法。\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FIGURE","captionHref":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.19","captionName":"Figure 3.19 ","captionBody":[{"body":"\n\t    使用前、后指针将队列作为一个列表实现。\n\t  ","tag":"#text"}]}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p7","child":[{"body":"\n    为了定义队列操作，我们使用下面的\n    函数,\n    这使我们能够选择并修改队列的前指针和后指针：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":1,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHToEwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQ8AnGsgfQAcz6AKARwIFN+ASlABvUPT5kC9WgAs+AQwAmPfkIDcoAL65CpSjXGL6bDqoF9hYiVJmgyCigBtzG7buLlqtAM6TmDEymXLwWADSgFGR8ALZWoH4s8squfBFRsYKaOvieBr7+Egom7CFqaZHRcaIJ-g7OqelVWe7YJDQ+ZKDcoAC8oKyOXACMEZhZ2IkBjEQspTwRACzj6gCQ+DNzZtxZQA","body":"function front_ptr(queue) { return head(queue); }\n\nfunction rear_ptr(queue) { return tail(queue); }\n\nfunction set_front_ptr(queue, item) { set_head(queue, item); }\n\nfunction set_rear_ptr(queue, item) { set_tail(queue, item); } "}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p8","child":[{"body":"\n    现在我们可以实现实际的队列操作。我们将认为队列为空当且仅当其前指针为空列表：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":2,"eval":true,"prependLength":9,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHToEwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQ8AnGsgfQAcz6AKARwIFN+ASlABvUPT5kC9WgAs+AQwAmPfkIDcoAL65CpSjXGL6bDqoF9hYiVJmgyCigBtzG7buLlqtAM6TmDEymXLwWADSgFGR8ALZWoH4s8squfBFRsYKaOvieBr7+Egom7CFqaZHRcaIJ-g7OqelVWe65+t6RPsyx7ACezKH8qfE20rQUXUQETi6BRCylwy05JDQ+ZKDcoAC8oKyOXFMzEZhZ2BPdMX0D5TxZQA","body":"function is_empty_queue(queue) { return is_null(front_ptr(queue)); } "},{"body":"\n    构造函数\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"make_queue"},{"body":"\n    返回一个初始为空的队列，该队列是一个对偶，其中的\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"head"},{"body":"\n    和\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"tail"},{"body":"\n    均为空列表：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":3,"eval":true,"prependLength":9,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHToEwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQ8AnGsgfQAcz6AKARwIFN+ASlABvUPT5kC9WgAs+AQwAmPfkIDcoAL65CpSjXGL6bDqoF9hYiVJmgyCigBtzG7buLlqtAM6TmDEymXLwWADSgFGR8ALZWoH4s8squfBFRsYKaOvieBr7+Egom7CFqaZHRcaIJ-g7OqelVWe65+t6gMQoA1nzMofyc8TbStKyOXEQETk4RUzMtOSQ0PmSg3KAAvJ09fQN8Q+r4jEQspTxZQA","body":"function make_queue() { return pair(null, null); } "},{"body":"\n    为了选择队列前部的元素，我们返回由前指针指示的对偶的\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"head"},{"body":"\n    ：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":4,"eval":true,"prependLength":11,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHToEwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQ8AnGsgfQAcz6AKARwIFN+ASlABvUPT5kC9WgAs+AQwAmPfkIDcoAL65CpSjXGL6bDqoF9hYiVJmgyCigBtzG7buLlqtAM6TmDEymXLwWADSgFGR8ALZWoH4s8squfBFRsYKaOvieBr7+Egom7CFqaZHRcaIJ-g7OqelVWe65+t6RPsyx7ACezKH8qfE20rQUXUQETi6BRCylwy05el6GcyyDfMOi2KD7RrbjXT1k-VvDewfXBwD8oHz0jGXhoABEGwPloCQKM3xKUAAdyislAClop16oC2b0EVxu1wAXKBkipPostoIstgciQaD4yDDQABeUCsRxcCkULgARgimEEERQOM+F24WSAA","body":"function front_queue(queue) {\n    return is_empty_queue(queue)\n           ? error(queue, \"front_queue called with an empty queue\")\n           : head(front_ptr(queue));\n} "}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p9","child":[{"body":"\n    要在队列中插入一项，我们遵循的方法，其结果在\n    图 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.20","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.20"},{"body":"中所示。\n    首先创建一个新的对偶，其\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"head"},{"body":"\n    为要插入的项，其\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"tail"},{"body":"\n    为空列表。如果队列最初为空，则将队列的前指针和后指针都设为这个新对偶；否则，我们修改队列中最后一个对偶，使其指向新对偶，并将后指针也更新为该新对偶。\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FIGURE","captionHref":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.20","captionName":"Figure 3.20 ","captionBody":[{"body":"\n\t    使用","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"insert_queue(q, \"d\")"},{"body":"对图 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.19","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.19"},{"body":"中的队列进行操作的结果。\n\t  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":5,"eval":true,"prependLength":22,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHToEwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQ8AnGsgfQAcz6AKARwIFN+ASlABvUPT5kC9WgAs+AQwAmPfkIDcoAL65CpSjXGL6bDqoF9hYiVJmgyCigBtzG7buLlqtAM6TmDEymXLwWADSgFGR8ALZWoH4s8squfBFRsYKaOvieBr7+Egom7CFqaZHRcaIJ-g7OqelVWe65+t6RPsyx7ACezKH8qfE20rQUXUQETi6BRCylwy05el6GMQoA1nwD5ZwjkmOgrI5cUzMR507LHu2GSnxOkjuDfMOi2KBfkXignBPdGJ9XYWJYfb4Q0B8eiMMrhUAAIgeT2iIP4oBIChmfCUoAA7lFZKAFLQemReqBXgisp9vlooU4-ODIV9EgFGPNgo17I5ZhyFmZXoJhepaSzRnZXqKIToVnkOhQiH56CxXtyMtURGKMTQfGRQEQ+Hi2KdQABeY6nf5VS7Ta7S74UX7-Lpk-pqoVWbUQtlzAVw-iXI0mij0Gks1mFYxc15B40nUPhukMplaiO1Fj1FxFEqC8qCOMhsMOllsnMx8qFhPF7U6CES2hS7A5Ei6-XcACM5tAG22aLeNMVytVe07EQRCmpmm+2CH0JHoLHiIARlOIdhkc9+zwOzTN6iPbv1EA","body":"function insert_queue(queue, item) {\n    const new_pair = pair(item, null);\n    if (is_empty_queue(queue)) {\n        set_front_ptr(queue, new_pair);\n        set_rear_ptr(queue, new_pair);\n    } else {\n        set_tail(rear_ptr(queue), new_pair);\n        set_rear_ptr(queue, new_pair);\n    }\n    return queue;\n} "}]},{"tag":"TEXT","id":"#p10","child":[{"body":"\n    为了删除队列首部的项，我们只需修改前指针，使其现在指向队列中的第二项，这可以通过沿着第一个项的\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"tail"},{"body":"\n    指针找到（参见\n    图 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.21","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.21"},{"body":"）：","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FOOTNOTE_REF","id":"#footnote-link-1","body":"1","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#footnote-1"},{"tag":"FIGURE","captionHref":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.21","captionName":"Figure 3.21 ","captionBody":[{"body":"\n\t    对图 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.20","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#fig-3.20"},{"body":"中的队列使用","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"delete_queue(q)"},{"body":"操作的结果。\n\t  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":6,"eval":true,"prependLength":25,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHToEwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQ8AnGs