"\"","tag":"#text"},{"body":"It's all wrong!","tag":"#text"},{"body":"\" 他抱怨道。\n    \"","tag":"#text"},{"body":"The interpreter's response shows that the last item is inserted\n    into the queue twice.  And when I delete both items, the second\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"b"},{"body":" is still there, so the queue isn't\n    empty, even though it's supposed to be.","tag":"#text"},{"body":"\"\n    Eva Lu Ator 认为 Ben 对正在发生的事情理解有误。\n    \"","tag":"#text"},{"body":"It's not that the\n    items are going into the queue twice,","tag":"#text"},{"body":"\" 她解释道。\n    \"","tag":"#text"},{"body":"It's just that the standard\n    JavaScript\n    printer doesn't know how to make sense of the queue representation.\n    If you want to see the queue printed correctly, you'll have to define\n    your own print\n    function\n    for queues.","tag":"#text"},{"body":"\"\n    解释 Eva Lu 所说的内容。具体来说，展示为什么 Ben 的示例会产生如此的打印结果。\n    定义一个\n    function","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"print_queue"},{"body":"\n    ，它接受一个队列作为输入，并打印队列中项的序列。\n    ","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":12,"eval":true,"prependLength":34,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHToEwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQBbAQwGsBTAfQEcCXuAKASlABvUACcWZAqNoAHBhVG8iBADYqANKGVr+AblABfXIVKUaoPKJpk2Msoq48WgkeMnTQACxYMAJr0duPUNjYnJqWnEGUVt7AO4g4TEJKVoyeRV4p2CjfDCzWgBnCTZLa1iHBJZNCjIWOhdQYptvPyzuGrqG-VyTcPNmtiiYu0qnTvrGwfSKTMDq0FrJntDTCMWiYtEbefaFpYbhbFAT0BIaQrItFgB3W3lRUABeUDkFXgPNbRU9Y9OKPCgD6FNj1OwAT04VT2-Bcf1Op0GZSINlGey+t3uCl+CIRg2GFXR1zub1EONOBlALBUxSOuMRJRmmQJaPm-AxJIe5Pp+J8Izi8w5WLJunhIQRblSoHmot6+XWFBBYLIkN2bKSko8irY314yNRAqqsJWeTW5l81Ik7DVRrp-0BwNBdAhUKcMLh9JOLFEVjGHVAACILSora7uGcGGoWL5QDdap5QAxaMrwdKqgHuYYqTSWHaeSV9YTBaAmXqrCii0bjWKJSkPDKxUY5WbZKIKBW1R7TpraL5FTIVAxwbxWv4ONXcudNlcOABGZ70ZjW6G-GRtjvQufBECvddkQoALi0qhU2HbWx2m9nmgDDAzorX7cvbq3+h3j5Rh9AAG1bwGvieAC6Z6bN6z58HON4AEb3tgH7gSwASztuYDwV+v53pov4wQBaiAcBwahmqyEPnuYaIa+oDvnu6EBjhx54UAA","body":"function print_queue(q) {\n    return display(head(q));\n} "}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 3.22","id":"#ex-3.22","child":[{"body":"\n    除了用一对指针来表示队列，我们还可以构建一个具有局部状态的队列，这种队列是一种\n    函数。局部状态将由指向普通列表开头和末尾的指针组成。因此，\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"make_queue"},{"body":"函数\n    将具有如下形式：\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":true,"eval":false,"body":"\nfunction make_queue() {\n    let front_ptr = $\\ldots$;\n    let rear_ptr = $\\ldots$;\n    $\\langle{}$内部函数的声明$\\rangle$\n    function dispatch(m) {$\\ldots$}\n    return dispatch;\n}\n      "},{"body":"\n    完成\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"make_queue"},{"body":"\n    的定义，并使用这种表示法给出队列操作的实现。\n    ","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":13,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=3&-3Tx5vP32NttDnt+l9avFEj1UjwtjsQTcZANQOwnFM7Ai6lNvORdk4LBCkv8LjCgUdrmDwQlCSlgiS4XxQZ8hoNhtkxnkOLEjHMquiwXcHq1nuRyjyFlYPhSZNNPMcAEQAMQASgB5AByABVQEodOF2KxQJsKAALUA6TTCgSgMVy8lfJEotE1KXfbr-VI40h4rq-Hp2pnDZmONm5TQ+Pi8WaVcV8r6sQo+Jw6ASdH5-fz+0BBrKjUNsBM6chKY0WLSSz4NJqaLRBQLBOW8KYzV5mOUYgD8+Um0yj8wxAC5tLX65zXNzo22wZ3R6cW+wB0O6-WhaURXPJ19OyuXmKFzWl6A5eHI+uO6Bj77d2DBzK1MctBc5QBVHh6HhqTagNQ+aaF8agABaADQAAEUgcBYAAQQ1aBKFtRks2GStmnzApDiLY0oiGEN-0bHs5wsMULiWMtYxkZDNDFCwG27ZsbSsE5liw+Rc3-GdxzeMVy3qVwq2taNqPY9cGOubDWLyC9e0sLiyJ4xoUKoo8I0vCcROY7AlA0Ao3GMVJdAMAjrkkgjjD6UB8EkgpB3aJxsDwuiBOMR8dHg7BjKo0yInMsBLMHABtOUXOJdIAF07NoqSFicw9aFc9zHLMizlPIKzQACoK0rlWLgvCEKwqEjyjOSkzEp85LUoC7LLicEKgA","body":"// 由 GitHub 用户 devinryu 提供\n\t  \nfunction make_queue() {\n    let front_ptr = null;\n    let rear_ptr = null;\n    function is_empty_queue() {\n        return is_null(front_ptr);\n    }\n    function insert_queue(item) {\n        let new_pair = pair(item, null);\n        if (is_empty_queue()) {\n            front_ptr = new_pair;\n            rear_ptr = new_pair;\n        } else {\n            set_tail(rear_ptr, new_pair);\n            rear_ptr = new_pair;\n        }\n    }\n    function delete_queue() {\n        if (is_empty_queue()) {\n            error(\"FRONT called with an empty queue\");\n        } else {\n            front_ptr = tail(front_ptr);\n        }\n    }\n    function print_queue() {\n        display(front_ptr);\n    }\n    function dispatch(m) {\n        return m === \"insert_queue\"\n        ? insert_queue\n        : m === \"delete_queue\"\n        ? delete_queue\n        : m === \"is_empty_queue\"\n        ? is_empty_queue\n        : m === \"print_queue\"\n        ? print_queue\n        : error(m, \"Unknow operation -- DISPATCH\");\n    }\n    return dispatch;\n}\nfunction insert_queue(queue, item) {\n    return queue(\"insert_queue\")(item);\n}\nfunction delete_queue(queue) {\n    return queue(\"delete_queue\")();\n}\nfunction print_queue(queue) {\n    return queue(\"print_queue\")();\n} "}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 3.23","id":"#ex-3.23","child":[{"body":"\n    一个","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EM","child":[{"body":"双端队列","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"\n    (\"","tag":"#text"},{"body":"双端队列","tag":"#text"},{"body":"\") 是一种序列，在这种序列中可以在\n    \n\t在前端或在\n      \n    后端插入和删除元素。\n    双端队列的操作包括构造函数\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"make_deque"},{"body":",\n    谓词\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"is_empty_deque"},{"body":",\n    \n    选择器\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"front_deque"},{"body":"\n    和\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"rear_deque"},{"body":",\n    以及修改操作\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"front_insert_deque"},{"body":",\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"front_delete_deque"},{"body":",\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"rear_insert_deque"},{"body":",\n      \n    和\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"rear_delete_deque"},{"body":".\n      \n    请展示如何使用对偶（pair）表示法表示双端队列，并给出这些操作的具体实现。","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"FOOTNOTE_REF","id":"#footnote-link-2","body":"2","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#footnote-2"},{"body":"\n    所有操作均应在\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"body":"$\\Theta(1)$","tag":"LATEX"},{"body":"\n    步内完成。\n    ","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":14,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=3&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlAZgHToEwChslIMeRgzYqCdpoBIWgjK6gDiAlgC4ASArgEaiAUroOxGoAxgDYBTAIYA7AJzjQgBeNA2fLYAZs1G96tAPajQAW2EBrQQH0AJoICOzQQAoAlKADe2UM9AAnQfWautAB2G1XK1Fmfn4AGlBg0JsAbmwAX1wlFTVNUAVXTXpDH3pA0wtBO0cXNw8vLQALEWMrAstYhKTlVQ0td2FXHLy68waHJxd3T29Qen9+XsLGxMUW1K0AZw9DDKzu-L7BCIZBbWLB52Xs6uFa+u3QXf242eTWtOPDDq7czcKd+j2D0qfx2kmF0+31uzRSbSui0Me1yAE8TFspv0SkNyqNaFCopM1qJsm8kUUbIdSqUAPxjVyWQYASBcAC5IYYsVYXhsCTYic5ac5yXkqVz6elhPxlqC5uC0hjDJojNcEYV2QNSsMKulMri2Rc7ABeXVlTqarYzMEPLQ47K0UTLVzZC4E4H7JUufCAf3kOIAz5UAAHKAKjlAJ-agDcFQAa2oAKhUAskqARBVAODGgAiU4m8TSLeiRQQAdxy-lcoG1oD8ASsucC1wiWJsxZC-EapVoClAVilMPo8LtWp+JKOK3Nho+ybTBcrbdAT1Z+KBPfTAX7znioEEIsETrbfwmQVT49cEU7I6Nk5J+EAYDoRmOAPujAHb+gC45McF4m-Fb-SanWqbnot4urvtxAeDjvqvHPrav3sMx3RI7nmCFO1MIQvnlSxFRRZxq1rettDhGDrBbBcSUEVxMneSwIgAIgg2cPCMC5QEAaojAC8vQAQt0AGeVAHuvQB8NMAdCVAGAYjgCOAmc5yuBQ6yhGVDDlZtt0wm9sifPDLhLD8ByHERXj-btZOvVERi0C45KnHjlnElwnik+0xmXIyWx3ZU0U0rZtNAECTQWfUukta1bURUdrlbBCawE6EUMbND2S8kl4ytJNRDfDMsxzDN81iotInLUtEuiWyJNWH8u3wy8gLSgyVmHZTsoiwCJ1s6dZz0+DdzAPccoCUAaMPaNTzPQAAc0AOBUfUAYUVAAJfNTnFCxN6szbMCzivMEsK6SOTLVKBq-bI7xZRSsqKAC1ws-Lsmm4ySs28qmnFU0nIRKCyPco1MMQ3yGybS7pmC0psNw4yCNZSDSLQyjaMY1iOK48rdPnatfKEkSHoaJ7toy9YtxUpK8vbHbVvh4rEYWlVRi04kKt46rSnwQAXs0ABtNTreUB2q670+qaqNY0-BSDTRy5lofFbmaKwkOSRsoNNAHHShAoA","body":"// 解决方案由 GitHub 用户 clean99 提供\nfunction make_deque() {\n    return pair(null, null);\n}\n\nfunction front_ptr(deque) {\n    return head(deque);\n}\n\nfunction rear_ptr(deque) {\n    return tail(deque);\n}\n\nfunction set_front_ptr(deque, item) {\n    set_head(deque, item);\n}\n\nfunction set_rear_ptr(deque, item) {\n    set_tail(deque, item);\n}\n\nfunction is_empty_deque(deque) {\n    return is_null(front_ptr(deque))\n           ? true\n  \t   : is_null(rear_ptr(deque))\n  \t   ? true\n  \t   : false;\n}\n\nfunction is_one_item_deque(deque) {\n    return front_ptr(deque) === rear_ptr(deque);\n}\n\nfunction front_insert_deque(deque, item) {\n    // 使用另一个对偶存储前向指针\n    const new_pair = pair(pair(item, null), null);\n    if (is_empty_deque(deque)) {\n        set_front_ptr(deque, new_pair);\n        set_rear_ptr(deque, new_pair);\n    } else {\n        set_tail(new_pair, front_ptr(deque));\n        // 将前向指针设置为 new_pair\n        set_tail(head(front_ptr(deque)), new_pair);\n        set_front_ptr(deque, new_pair);\n    }\n}\n\nfunction front_delete_deque(deque) {\n    if (is_empty_deque(deque)) {\n        error(deque, \"front_delete_deque 被空的双端队列调用\");\n    } else if(is_one_item_deque(deque)) {\n        set_front_ptr(deque, null);\n        set_rear_ptr(deque, null);\n        return deque;\n    } else {\n        set_front_ptr(deque, tail(front_ptr(deque)));\n        return deque;\n    }\n}\n\nfunction rear_insert_deque(deque, item) {\n    if (is_empty_deque(deque)) {\n        const new_pair = pair(pair(item, null), null);\n        set_front_ptr(deque, new_pair);\n        set_rear_ptr(deque, new_pair);\n    } else {\n        // 将 new_pair 的前向指针设置为最后一个元素\n        const new_pair = pair(pair(item, rear_ptr(deque)), null);\n        set_tail(rear_ptr(deque), new_pair);\n        set_rear_ptr(deque, new_pair);\n    }\n}\n\nfunction rear_delete_deque(deque) {\n    if (is_empty_deque(deque)) {\n        error(deque, \"rear_delete_deque 被空的双端队列调用\");\n    } else if(is_one_item_deque(deque)) {\n        set_front_ptr(deque, null);\n        set_rear_ptr(deque, null);\n        return deque;\n    } else {\n        // 更新 rear_ptr 为最后一个元素的前向指针\n        set_rear_ptr(deque, tail(head(rear_ptr(deque))));\n        return deque;\n    }\n} "}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-1","count":1,"href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#footnote-link-1","child":[{"body":"如果第一个项是队列中的最后一项，则删除后前指针将变为空列表，从而标志该队列为空；我们不必担心更新后指针，因为它仍指向已删除的项，而\n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"is_empty_queue"},{"body":"\n    仅检查前指针。","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-2","count":2,"href":"/sicpjs/3.3.2#footnote-link-2","child":[{"body":"注意不要使解释器尝试打印包含循环结构的数据。（参见练习 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"3.13","href":"/sicpjs/3.3.1#ex-3.13"},{"body":"。）","tag":"#text"}]}]